"blokadministrationssiden."

msgid ""
"For more information, see the <a "
"href=\":layout-builder-documentation\">online documentation for the "
"Layout Builder module</a>."
msgstr ""
"Du kan få flere oplysninger i <a "
"href=\":layout-builder-documentation\">onlinedokumentationen for "
"Layout Builder-modulet</a>."

msgid "Configure any layout"
