"<code>@version</code>. Se <a href=\":url\">dokumentationen om "
"Composer</a> for mere information, eller brug denne kommando til at "
"tilføje Composer til dit projekt: <code>composer require "
"\"composer/composer:@version\"</code>."

msgid ""
"The path to Composer is set in configuration, which is no longer "
"supported. To fix this, add <code>composer/composer</code> to your "
"project's dependencies by running <code>composer require "
"'composer/composer:@version'</code>, <em>or</em> add the following "
"line to <code>settings.php</code>: "
"<code>$settings['package_manager_composer_path'] = "
"'@composer_path';</code>. See <a href=\":url\">this change record</a> "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"Stien til Composer er indstillet i konfigurationen, hvilket ikke "
"længere understøttes. For at løse dette skal du tilføje "
"<code>composer/composer</code> til dit projekts afhængigheder ved at "
"køre <code>composer require 'composer/composer:@version'</code>, "
"<em>eller</em> tilføje følgende linje til <code>settings.php</code>: "
"<code>$settings['package_manager_composer_path'] = "
"'@composer_path';</code>. Se <a href=\":url\">denne ændringspost</a> "
"for mere information."

msgid "Path to <code>rsync</code> is configured"
